the blade films are based on the fictional marvel comics character of the same name , portrayed by wesley snipes .   they were written by david s. goyer , based on the comics by marv wolfman , and gene colan .   the three films were directed by stephen norrington , guillermo del toro and goyer respectively , and distributed by new line cinema .   the character was created in 1973 for marvel comics by writer marv wolfman and artist gene colan and was a supporting character in the 1970s comic tomb of dracula .   in the comic , blade 's mother was bitten by a vampire while she was in labor with blade .